      "cooked": "<p>The following photos are to clarify the ability and method we use to mount Liquid TV into one of the Vessel cases we use in our studio. Right angle RCA sync cables connect from the Sync Out on Visual Cortex to Liquid TV and then again from Sync Out on Liquid TV to the Sync Bus board on Vessel.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6.jpeg\" title=\"d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6_2_690x387.jpeg\" alt=\"41542229_329508804470011_703323404643598336_n\" width=\"690\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6_2_690x387.jpeg, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6_2_1035x580.jpeg 1.5x, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6_2_1380x774.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">d4fc01a6325802428b539cc1ca6decd8d5077ad6.jpeg</span><span class=\"informations\">3548\u00d71995 453 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37.jpeg\" title=\"27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37_2_690x387.jpeg\" alt=\"41659959_334982663905187_2910415099858518016_n\" width=\"690\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37_2_690x387.jpeg, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37_2_1035x580.jpeg 1.5x, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37_2_1380x774.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">27f535568da2c3749c17b550872df1900ef01d37.jpeg</span><span class=\"informations\">3548\u00d71995 524 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
