      "cooked": "<p>Hey Jonah!<br>\nIn relation to this subject, the mounting depth for My Liquid TV seems to be a few millimeters off from the length that\u2019s shown on the LZX website. Because of this, my TV doesn\u2019t fit at all on the top right hand corner of my Vessel (next to the fan).<br>\nI\u2019ve provided two side view images below of my TV module. You can see how the Video sockets + the PCB extends out more than the picture that you\u2019ve provided of yours.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601.jpeg\" title=\"IMG_20180909_152457.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601_2_375x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_20180909_152457\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601_2_375x500.jpeg, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601_2_562x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601_2_750x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/61185deb5939ff583894b3b26b23751d03b0a601_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_20180909_152457.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">3024\u00d74032 2.43 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2.jpeg\" title=\"MVIMG_20180912_213330.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2_2_374x500.jpeg\" alt=\"MVIMG_20180912_213330\" width=\"374\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2_2_374x500.jpeg, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2_2_561x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2_2_748x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/optimized/1X/ef276a239d3cc2dd6dc99dad0fea0863ab5199e2_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">MVIMG_20180912_213330.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">2138\u00d72851 1.55 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
